# Blueskybot — Feed Configuration
#
# Add one feed per line. Empty lines and lines starting with # are ignored.
#
# Format:
#   URL
#   URL | Title
#   provider://id
#   provider://id | Title
#
# The title is optional. If provided, it prefixes the Bluesky post.
#
# ─── Built-in providers ────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# rss (default):     any http/https URL works without a prefix.
# sr-api:            Sveriges Radio news API — use the programid as the id.
#                    Browse programs at https://sverigesradio.se/
#
# See providers/_template.mjs for how to add your own provider.
#
# ─── Examples ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
#   https://example.com/feed.xml
#   https://example.com/feed.xml | Example News
#   sr-api://83    | Ekot
#   sr-api://2795  | Radiosporten

https://example.com/rss-feed-1.xml | Example Feed 1
https://example.com/rss-feed-2.xml | Example Feed 2

# sr-api://83   | Ekot
# sr-api://2795 | Radiosporten
